{"id": "ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ", "rating": 3.9, "userRatingCount": 30, "displayName": {"text": "adidas Flagship Store West Hollywood", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Retail store featuring the brand's signature athletic footwear, clothes & accessories.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQMTVHUE1BEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love this Adidas Flagship Store, got another new pair of amazing shoes here my Adidas Tokyo... and the Staff are friendly and accomodating, i forgot the name of particular girl that assisted me, shes really nice, but all of them are nice, they have wide range of products and shoes at this store, great location.. cant wait to visit again ❤️👍", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love this Adidas Flagship Store, got another new pair of amazing shoes here my Adidas Tokyo... and the Staff are friendly and accomodating, i forgot the name of particular girl that assisted me, shes really nice, but all of them are nice, they have wide range of products and shoes at this store, great location.. cant wait to visit again ❤️👍", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "MAV", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109829172391046444585/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK3u3I26axnX8zRJwNEMayyaO-qjMZE1o30CZQdWjcIZVMvPM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-12-06T08:19:18.433806Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQMTVHUE1BEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQMTVHUE1BEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2bff4988ead29:0xe4a152b95fbd843e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORFkwMU1jRFYxTTJoUUxXTlpkVk0xUkZSWFRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Omg. I love this store it always has the best drops. I live in Palmdale and I really hate that they never answer the phone for me to see if they have new stuff before I come. Is there correct number listed. I’m tryna shop right now! Super irritated great staff!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Omg. I love this store it always has the best drops. I live in Palmdale and I really hate that they never answer the phone for me to see if they have new stuff before I come. Is there correct number listed. I’m tryna shop right now! Super irritated great staff!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tomisha Johnson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106650237618564731379/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJG9VgZnOmi4VY0QNsWsSckdEmjLCXOyVkUzLs8YQZHzrLQ5Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-11T00:44:39.924349276Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORFkwMU1jRFYxTTJoUUxXTlpkVk0xUkZSWFRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tORFkwMU1jRFYxTTJoUUxXTlpkVk0xUkZSWFRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bff4988ead29:0xe4a152b95fbd843e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oWU1tZFJiVU5FV1hCell6RlFXa0p4U0cxT2IxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came to pick up an online clothing order yesterday, in a smaller size than I wanted bc online Adidas website said they didn't have anymore in a size Medium that I wanted, but I loved this one particular jacket so much that I was willing to buy a smaller size.... come to find, when I randomly asked the woman at the cash wrap just as I was about to pay if they ever expected medium sizes back in, she said \"I think we have one in stock\", and sure enough, she found me the size I was looking for!! Thank god I asked, but she said when you order online for store pickup, it may say \"sold out\" of a size online bc the website is basing it off of online stock, but the store might have the size in stock, so always doublecheck (confusing, I know, by anyways, always doublecheck store stock) !! She saved the day, plus all staff were really nice there, and the stuff out was cool too, especially the Fear of God and Y3 stuff.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came to pick up an online clothing order yesterday, in a smaller size than I wanted bc online Adidas website said they didn't have anymore in a size Medium that I wanted, but I loved this one particular jacket so much that I was willing to buy a smaller size.... come to find, when I randomly asked the woman at the cash wrap just as I was about to pay if they ever expected medium sizes back in, she said \"I think we have one in stock\", and sure enough, she found me the size I was looking for!! Thank god I asked, but she said when you order online for store pickup, it may say \"sold out\" of a size online bc the website is basing it off of online stock, but the store might have the size in stock, so always doublecheck (confusing, I know, by anyways, always doublecheck store stock) !! She saved the day, plus all staff were really nice there, and the stuff out was cool too, especially the Fear of God and Y3 stuff.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "H Ngo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117500224285195981227/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKja7ECsM1Ba2Za9CYfZyyotT3f_AoVuzDwLD5DHU8nlkFALw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-07T22:21:22.486538123Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oWU1tZFJiVU5FV1hCell6RlFXa0p4U0cxT2IxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oWU1tZFJiVU5FV1hCell6RlFXa0p4U0cxT2IxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bff4988ead29:0xe4a152b95fbd843e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjelZXNDBSbTFxUVhOb1NURnpkR3MyWkZCcGMyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Drive 1 hour to this location to find items not available, also did a return that was mailed back to another state and taking my refund into over a week to get to the other state 10 days later still waiting for my refund .this new policy shipping returns back  Adidas will lose a long term faithful customer", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Drive 1 hour to this location to find items not available, also did a return that was mailed back to another state and taking my refund into over a week to get to the other state 10 days later still waiting for my refund .this new policy shipping returns back  Adidas will lose a long term faithful customer", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tweet Roberts", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102776426323147991694/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgKFETbMFi6UEfsZkKT9pDnmrcFuPutxd5oOO1rMFjiiTBEFI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-28T05:19:43.319664626Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjelZXNDBSbTFxUVhOb1NURnpkR3MyWkZCcGMyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjelZXNDBSbTFxUVhOb1NURnpkR3MyWkZCcGMyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bff4988ead29:0xe4a152b95fbd843e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJKa2OmPS_woARPoS9X7lSoeQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUQ3ck92REh3EAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Hard to discover from the outside but worth stepping in: the adidas flagship store! Very fashionable, the shoes are on a „catwalk“. Staff was ext